data.description: Step into this inviting 3-bed, 2-bath Clayton-built manufactured home, resting on a foundation and generous lot. This 2021 gem offers modern comforts with a master suite boasting a private bathroom with dual vanities, large shower, and walk-in closet. The home screams charming, with its exposed beams and spacious doorways. Discover practicality with a large walk-in pantry and abundant storage, including plenty of floating shelves/built-ins.  Outside, a fenced 6-ft chain link backyard awaits, providing security and space for outdoor enjoyment. Embrace the ample room of the large lot, perfect for various activities. Notably, this home features solar panels, adding eco-friendliness and cost-efficiency to its appeal. Experience the blend of comfort, functionality, and sustainability in this family-friendly home crafted for you!
